item.description: SoftLayer_Network_LBaaS_LoadBalancer Service Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Network_LBaaS_LoadBalancer type presents a structure containing attributes of a load balancer, and its related objects including listeners, pools and members. Local accountId The account this load balancer belongs to. Type: integer address Address (Host name) of a load balancer. Type: string createDate Specifies when a load balancer was created. Type: dateTime description Description of a load balancer.
